    "Generative adversarial attack and defense strategyWithin the generative adversarial attack and defense strategy category, 7 of the 51 papers focused on two subcategories: the papers that used text datasets and the papers that used image and graph datasets.",
    "These papers explore how to generate an adversarial attack and how to defend against this attack.In the field of text datasets, two papers were published.",
    "Zhan et al. [102] presented MalPatch as a method of adversarial attack against DNN-based malware detection systems.",
